Language,Detection,API,is,a,free,service,that,determines,what,potential,languages,a,word,or,phrase,may,be,written,in,The,API,returns,values,for,an,array,of,viable,language,codes,true,or,false,reliability,and,a,confidence,score,It,supports,both,GET,and,POST,requests,although,POST,is,recommend,for,larger,requests,It,is,also,compatible,with,Google,Translate,input,and,output